Gives marriage information for Thomas and Sarah Ashley.
Yr of birth 1786; Married 1808 in Mansfield; Wife Sarah Ashley.
Birth year 1786 in Blackwell, Derby; Age 75 living in Mansfield Woodhouse in 1861.
Christen date 3 May 1786 in Blackwell, Derby; Father Thomas Humphrey, Mother Ann.

Yes, the surname was misspelled by the clerk, but the common spelling of that time was that shown for the father, "Humphrey". No suffix was attached, such as "Sr". That was used by later historians to satisfy their own purposes.
